{"tid":582632,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日晚餐] 番薯燜豬肉","createTime":"2018-03-06T10:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T00:15:30.000Z","uid":43041,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb7da55f3c1a08d65c05d26c7aaa0bd3c63cdbd","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"今次想挑戰既食品黎自Elder Scrolls系列既世界<br />\n原本叫Horker and Ash yam stew<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/171700_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F171700_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=22d73277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過以上兩樣野食我地依個世界都無，所以拎豬肉同紫番薯黎代替<br />\n結果 唉味道雖然唔錯但賣相唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170543_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170543_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8f7f10a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豬肉切件，薯仔切粒，紫番薯切大塊，洋蔥切碎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170620_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170620_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d575aaec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用rosemary, thyme, basil, garlic powder, salt, pepper腌豬肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=73275689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炒豬肉，炒到表面有焦就可以落洋蔥炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170903_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170903_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f4386968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炒到變色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e3e6aeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落雞湯同水，加入番薯+薯仔<br />\n較細d火滾佢15至20分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/171408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F171408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c500ece9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落椰奶 再等佢滾<br />\n當收水到鍾意既濃杰度就可以食啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/171606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F171606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7bbdf416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唉 我都知個賣相唔吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過味道唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食譜係度：<a href=\"https://tastesoftamriel.tumblr.com/post/165347432243/horker-and-ash-yam-stew-the-first-time-i-tried\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftastesoftamriel.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F165347432243%2Fhorker-and-ash-yam-stew-the-first-time-i-tried&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ea290a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tastesoftamriel.tumblr.com/post/165347432243/horker-and-ash-yam-stew-the-first-time-i-tried</a>"},{"pid":"11a220c29d9ddd2b69643816803008c018128c0e","tid":582632,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"蕃薯呀 誰都喜歡你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff523cd4ca4042e99f3fad98a2b87ef43f1c051","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a220c29d9ddd2b69643816803008c018128c0e","tid":582632,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"蕃薯呀 誰都喜歡你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解係叮噹歌詞"},{"pid":"d4eefee00da72af796fc11586e58641aa8ac404f","tid":582632,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"太多汁？<br />\n肉可以揀啲肥啲？<br />\n<br />\n食落口感如何？"},{"pid":"059af7314f062d8c15f2e271b80395c020b3f2de","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4eefee00da72af796fc11586e58641aa8ac404f","tid":582632,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"太多汁？<br />\n肉可以揀啲肥啲？<br />\n<br />\n食落口感如何？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"stew黎，本來就應該係半湯半汁咁上，所以原圖都係用碗裝。但我搵唔到啱既中文黎形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口感普普通通咁啦，全部材料都幾lum，因為煲左幾耐下 (半個鐘以上)"},{"pid":"e06e1146b528f0048eaa55817258dbdd2496eb92","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"059af7314f062d8c15f2e271b80395c020b3f2de","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4eefee00da72af796fc11586e58641aa8ac404f","tid":582632,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"太多汁？<br />\n肉可以揀啲肥啲？<br />\n<br />\n食落口感如何？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"stew黎，本來就應該係半湯半汁咁上，所以原圖都係用碗裝。但我搵唔到啱既中文黎形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口感普普通通咁啦，全部材料都幾lum，因為煲左幾耐下 (半個鐘以上)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:24:04.000Z","msg":"係其實 我唔知咩肉先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見到有無骨既豬柳就揀左佢"},{"pid":"08e3e96f478444c9f552b9303930855071634925","tid":582632,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"睇到標題已經吞緊口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4aef9f9f097e566aa33001ab0ff2a8e758638b4","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e3e96f478444c9f552b9303930855071634925","tid":582632,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"睇到標題已經吞緊口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"唔會見到依個組合好怪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我如果唔係因為隻game真係唔會諗到咁食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f71d597b67f03addf5fbedb3e8a360426de9600","tid":582632,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"805d3f163e6dbf62a374f13d21959fe44acc9520","tid":582632,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇到標題已經吞緊口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔會見到依個組合好怪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我如果唔係因為隻game真係唔會諗到咁食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會呀反而好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd21b80774b437f8a9b8c13b179189b1142863c","tid":582632,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f71d597b